Mavin Records founder, Michael Collins Ajereh also known as Don Jazzy is a happy-go-lucky fellow who just loves having fun and being playful.










The music producer shared a video of stepping out rocking a complete Dior outfit and he self-appraised, saying that he is looking good.
Don Jazzy could be seen dancing while walking out of his house and he declared that he is an orobo who looks good in Dior.
Sharing the video clip, he captioned; ”Bad man is an orobo.”
